=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]
Ezra [ https://substack.com/redirect/3fda8272-9e28-4c05-8f5b-b0c0853c019e?j=
=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] is on a=
 mission to detect cancer early for everyone in the world. The company offe=
rs full-body MRI scans in order to catch cancer earlier to increase the odd=
s of beating it.=C2=A0
I recently did an Ezra scan myself, and while it was nerve-wracking to face=
 cancer, confirming that I=E2=80=99m cancer-free was a priceless relief. My=
 scan took 60 minutes, but Ezra just received FDA clearance for the world=
=E2=80=99s first 30-minute full body MRI to screen for cancer. It=E2=80=99s=
 faster, more affordable, and just as accurate thanks to Ezra Flash AI.=C2=
=A0
Book your Ezra scan [ https://substack.com/redirect/7e877010-29c4-4b9c-957b=
